    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "so you're saying it's just a mild thing? i phrased it as \"usually mild\" but it sounds like you think the interaction isn't a big deal as long as i space them out. i really don't want to go back to the doctor for a follow up if i don't have to, so are you sure i don't need to stop the simvastatin while i'm on the antibiotics?",
